# Input

```scss
@keyframes fade{$stop:50%;#{$stop}{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}

```


# Formatted

```scss
@keyframes fade {
	$stop: 50%;
	#{$stop} {
		opacity: 0;
	}
	to {
		opacity: 1;
	}
}

```
